---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Affiliate Disclosure • Fin Sanctuary"
  description="Read the Fin Sanctuary affiliate disclosure and how affiliate links may appear alongside aquarium guides and recommendations."
>
  <main>
    <section class="border-b border-primary/10 bg-[linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(1,133,174,0.08),rgba(243,239,238,0.55))] dark:border-white/8 dark:bg-[linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(13,175,188,0.14),rgba(2,6,23,0.95))]">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-6 py-10 md:py-12">
        <div class="text-[0.72rem] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.28em] text-primary/75">Affiliate Disclosure</div>
        <h1 class="mt-5 font-bold tracking-tight text-primary">How affiliate links may be used on Fin Sanctuary.</h1>
        <p class="mt-6 max-w-3xl text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-200">
          Fin Sanctuary is built to educate first. Some pages may also include affiliate links when they support the topic naturally and help keep the site running.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-6 py-10">
      <article class="rounded-[2rem] border border-primary/10 bg-white px-7 py-8 shadow-[0_24px_80px_-55px_rgba(1,133,174,0.42)] dark:border-white/8 dark:bg-slate-900 md:px-9">
        <div class="space-y-7 text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">
          <section>
            <h2 class="font-semibold tracking-tight text-primary">Affiliate Relationships</h2>
            <p class="mt-3">Some links on Fin Sanctuary may be affiliate links. If a reader clicks one of those links and makes a purchase, Fin Sanctuary may earn a commission at no additional cost to the buyer.</p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="font-semibold tracking-tight text-primary">Editorial Priority</h2>
            <p class="mt-3">Recommendations should remain editorial-first and practical-first. The purpose of a guide or recommendation is to help readers make better aquarium decisions, not to push products that do not fit the setup.</p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="font-semibold tracking-tight text-primary">Where Affiliate Links May Appear</h2>
            <p class="mt-3">Affiliate links may appear in long-form guides, product comparison sections, recommendation flows, maintenance pages, and supporting buying lists where those links clearly match the subject being discussed.</p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="font-semibold tracking-tight text-primary">No Guarantee or Endorsement Promise</h2>
            <p class="mt-3">A product link does not mean every reader should buy that product. Fit, tank size, livestock needs, and maintenance habits still matter. Readers should review product details carefully before purchasing.</p>
          </section>
        </div>
      </article>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>
